text: Namrata ShresthaOn the Wave Magazine's Cover (born June 14, 1986) is a famous Nepalese model and actress known from her debut movie Sano Sansar in 2008. She gained fame with her romantic character in the movies November Rain and Mero Euta Saathi Chha. She has won many National Film Awards. She is well recognized by her movies, music videos, televisions ads, theatre productions, and modelling. She is ranked as the top actress of Nepal. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Nepalese movie actors Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models
